channel.title: [PI] Offering help
channel.description:
Hello, I am looking for a coder that is new to coding project insanity. I can teach you source coding plus client/cache editing. I will be on from(Moparscape time) 8 AM till 1 PM. If you are interested reply or send me a message.
[u]I don't want money nor other resources.[/u]
